'''Landing craft''' are boats and seagoing vessels used to convey a landing force (infantry and vehicles) from the sea to the shore during an amphibious assault. Most renowned are those used to storm the beaches of Normandy, the Mediterranean, and many Pacific islands during World War II.

In the game they provide [[Expedition/Introduction#Landing_Craft|bonuses to expedition incomes]] and damage bonuses to some [[Enemy_vessel#Bosses_.28Land_Bases.29|Land Based enemies]].